data.description: **Unbelievable Price Drop – Unleash the Potential of Your New Home or Investment!**  Seller's Enthusiasm Soars! Welcome to the Enchanting Palmetto Point Community.    Prepare to be Amazed by the Latest Jewel in Highly Coveted Palmetto Point! This extraordinary corner lot property boasts lush St. Augustine grass and mesmerizing palm trees, creating an idyllic outdoor haven. The residence showcases an alluring 3-bedroom, 3-bathroom layout with a den and an attached 3-car garage, offering an absolute dream living space.    This location truly embodies the quintessential Florida lifestyle. With an intelligently designed split floor plan that places the master bedroom off the kitchen, this home provides countless opportunities for personal retreats.    As you traverse the home, you'll be captivated by the exquisite tile flooring that elevates its overall allure. The generously sized master bedroom features a luxurious sauna and a private exit to the lanai, establishing a secluded paradise within your own abode. Venture outside to explore the extended lanai and the fenced-in yard, complete with top-tier security systems and cameras for an unparalleled peace of mind. Remarkably, the third bathroom is ingeniously situated in the garage, adding a distinctive touch to the property. Additionally, a 10x10 shed with shelving awaits for your storage needs, while extra refrigerator appliances are thoughtfully included for your convenience.    This residence exudes warmth and beckons your imaginative touch, offering limitless possibilities for personalization. The community is strategically located mere minutes away from I-75, I-275, US-41, and US-301, guaranteeing effortless journeys to the vibrant hubs of St. Pete, Tampa, Sarasota, and Anna Maria Island/Holmes Beach. Furthermore, you're tantalizingly close to indulgent shopping and dining experiences at the Ellenton Outlet Mall and Sarasota's University Town Center.    Don't let this incredible home slip from your grasp. With a seller who is positively charged with motivation, seize this unparalleled opportunity to immerse yourself in the pinnacle of Florida living. Secure your viewing appointment today and make this house your forever home!    With an exceptionally motivated seller, this extraordinary chance to possess your slice of paradise in Palmetto Point should never be allowed to fade away. Schedule your viewing today and make this your permanent sanctuary! We also have 4pt and Wind mitigation  reports.
